---------------------------------------------------------------(without shield pvp)
sweep_attack - attacking while walking, standing or crouching
critical_attack (crits) - strong attack landed while dropping and not sprinting (due to jump, fall or knockback dealt by other player)
sprint_reset_attack (w-tap) - strong attack landed immediately after stopping sprinting (this attack deals the most knockback)
                    (s-tap) - after every hit you let go off W and press S instantly

punish_critical_attack (p-crits) - landing crit while dropping after ememy blows you into the air
double_critting - critting opponent and p-critting as your opponent blows you up in air 
crit_chaining - landing crit continuously on every jump
combos - continuous strong attack with sprint reseting
upper-cut combo - you have to hit your opponent as you are jumping and instantly press S
sprint-cut combo - hitting your opponent is you are falling down and let go off W before you hit

jump reseting - pressing jump on the exact time when opponent hits you to barely take any knockback
hitselect - letting you opponent hit you first, and hit them back when you are in air (while holding down W)
